Text: Rajasthan Institute of Engineering and Technology (RIET ) https://www.rietjaipur.ac.in Rajasthan Institute of Engineering and Technology (RIET), located in Jaipur, is a prominent private engineering college in Rajasthan. The institute is known for its focus on technical education in various disciplines and offers undergraduate and postgradua te programs in engineering and management. Courses Offered: 1. B.Tech Programs (Undergraduate): o Mechanical Engineering o Civil Engineering o Computer Science Engineering o Electrical Engineering o Information Technology o Electronics & Communication Engineering 2. M.Tech Programs (Postgraduate): o Specializations such as Computer Science, Electrical Engineering, and more. 3. MBA (Postgraduate): o Offers MBA programs to students focusing on management skills integrated with technology. Admission Process: • B.Tech Admissions are primarily based on JEE Main scores, and state -level entrance exams like REAP (Rajasthan Engineering Admission Process) are also considered. • M.Tech Admissions are usually based on GATE scores. • MBA admissions consider exams like CAT/MAT and other state -level entrance exams. Infrastructure and Facilities: RIET is equipped with modern infrastructure, including: • Well-furnished laboratories • Library with an extensive collection of technical and research -related books • Hostel facilities for both boys and girls • Sports and extracurricular activities , fostering an all -rounded student experience. Placement: RIET has an active placement cell that helps students secure job opportunities with leading companies in sectors like IT, Manufacturing, and more. Notable recruiters include Infosys, Wipro, TCS, and many others. The placement record is supported by regular training, workshops, and industry interactions. Accreditation and Rankings: • RIET is affiliated with Rajasthan Technical University and is recognized by AICTE. • The institute has gained recognition in regional rankings for engineering colleges and maintains good industry connections for placement. Courses & Fees: 1. B.Tech Programs : o Duration : 4 years o Fees: ₹3.20 - ₹4.20 Lakhs (total for 4 years, depending on the specialization) 2. M.Tech Programs : o Duration : 2 years o Fees: ₹1.50 - ₹1.80 Lakhs (total for 2 years) 3. MBA: o Duration : 2 years o Fees: ₹2.00 - ₹2.50 Lakhs The fee structure may vary slightly based on the course, specialization, and additional facilities availed by the student. Ratings: • Careers360 Rating : The institute has a rating of 4.0/5, based on student reviews, infrastructure, faculty, and placements . • Placements : RIET has a dedicated placement cell that provides job opportunities in top companies. The average salary package ranges from ₹3.5 LPA to ₹5.5 LPA, while the highest packages can go up to ₹10 -12 LPA in some cases. Infrastructure: • Modern laboratories , fully-equipped with the latest technology for all branches. • Digital Library with a vast collection of books, research papers, and e -journals. • Hostel accommodation : Separate facilities for boys and girls, with good dining and recreation areas. • Sports facilities : The campus has various sports amenities to encourage extracurricular activities. • Wi-Fi campus , cafeteria, and medical facilities available. Additional Features: • Scholarships : RIET provides various merit -based scholarships and financial aid for students
